room_title: Escape room "The Hideout" by Escape Rooms Unlocked in Sarasota
room_description: This time, he’s robbed the First National Bank. The good news is you and your sheriff deputies have tracked down his secret hideout. We know the money is here somewhere, the only question is… where? You can already see the dust clouds kicking up from the horses the rest of Billy’s gang are riding in on. You have to locate the cash before they arrive or you may just have a showdown on your hands.
